OL,3,C'Beloved' Scottish Borders railway
OL,4,Ccampaigner dies at the age of 95
OL,6,F"Truly a life well lived, she gave so
OL,7,Fmuch time to the community, not just
OL,8,Fin terms of the railway campaigning
OL,9,F(well documented elsewhere), but a
OL,10,Fhuge contribution to tennis (in
OL,11,Fpartnership with our dad, Bob) and a
OL,12,Fwhole host of other campaigns and
OL,13,Fvolunteering roles over her lifetime,
OL,14,Ftoo many to list.
